{"tid":274321,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"28名立法會議員聯合動議彈劾梁振英","createTime":"2017-06-07T08:38:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-07T10:37:58.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7162b72327fcc51ce871286eee5f8680c34b44a9","tid":274321,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T08:38:53.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】28名立法會議員聯合動議彈劾行政長官梁振英。動議人公民黨楊岳橋表示，梁振英透過周浩鼎修改調查UGL專責委員會的研究範圍是瀆職，有必要委任獨立調查委員會調查事件。<br />\n<br />\n根據基本法第73條，議員聯合動議要在立法會大會經分組點票表決才會啟動調查程序，由終審法院首席法官擔任主席的獨立調查委員會調查。<br />\n<br />\n調查報告交回立法會後要得到三分二議員通過，而最終特首是否要被免職都要由中央政府決定。"},{"pid":"8e1d1f2e987fd15759283f80273ef3e06bcab2ef","tid":274321,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T08:39:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=223916\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D223916&d=iHYIvASeIYm3X8ZRBd4O1cPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=826a0d33\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D223916&h=e2e9d841\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=223916</a>"},{"pid":"9cc7593d75a4b3b2769b3e93f34ef8170e19c7fe","tid":274321,"uid":41245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T08:59:59.000Z","msg":"啫係收工啦"},{"pid":"79daa71b1f6536e29cabf25f0264fd4d47018505","tid":274321,"uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T09:02:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77c3b892f8c9e84bb2007b936b3f7acba7f06c81","tid":274321,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T10:12:14.000Z","msg":"犯聞最叻做大龍鳳 之後就對外話我地做左野算得上係對大眾交差 係賤制派玩野"},{"pid":"b08d1acfe7600634f5065113c6f8bea12056ab69","tid":274321,"uid":71453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T10:13:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>【Now新聞台】28名立法會議